  "name": "Breach Control",
  "description": "When inactive, the Breach control module uses field emitters in the same manner as a regular damage control unit. Once activated, it supercharges those field emitters to create waves of charge that ripple throughout the vessel, disrupting the efforts of any breacher teams before ultimately burning out the module.\n\nGrants a bonus to resistance for shield, armor, and hull.\n\nMay be activated to grant a significant resistance to Breacher Pod damage for a limited period of time. However, it will burn out after a single use.\n\nNote: Only one Damage Control can be fit at a given time.",
